WEBVTT

00:08:29.454 --> 00:08:31.557
that fundamentally need to change.

00:08:32.396 --> 00:08:35.570
First, we need to change our cities.

00:08:36.298 --> 00:08:41.711
By 2050, two thirds of our population
will live in cities.

00:08:42.298 --> 00:08:44.433
We need green cities.

00:08:45.092 --> 00:08:48.854
Second, we need to change
our energy system.

00:08:48.878 --> 00:08:52.584
The world economy
must sharply decarbonize,

00:08:52.608 --> 00:08:54.861
essentially in one generation.

00:08:56.050 --> 00:09:00.700
Third, we need to change
our production-consumption system.